    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Combine</strong> the parsley, garlic and 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(8 tbsp)</span>&nbsp;olive oil with a (stick) blender for the salsa verde</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong>&nbsp;generously with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p>Tip: For a lighter version replace the&nbsp;oil with&nbsp;water</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
