    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Season</strong> the pork steaks on both sides with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> 1-2 tbsp vegetable oil to a pan on a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> the oil is hot, add the pork and cook for 3 min on each side or until cooked through</p>",
